item.title: fifth
item.description: “Peace of mind produces right values, right values produce right thoughts. Right thoughts produce right actions and right actions produce work which will be a material reflection for others to see of the serenity at the center of it all.” ― Robert M. Pirsig, Zen and the Art of Motorcycle Maintenance

item.title: about
item.description: Put some content in Markdown format below the toml front-matter (the section marked by +++ before and after it) and then save it. Now, let’s add a new post. To do so enter the following: $ hugo new post/first.md The new file is located at content/post/first.md. It’s just begging to be spiced up, isn’t it?
